{
  "stem": "13313.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the point I'm trying to make is, so we walked on foot every morning to that school from where we were, and on the way, I fell in step with a local boy.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I would say he was about 12, 13 years old, maybe even more, much bigger than we were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- because we walked the same way for whatever reason, under the same direction, we-- we started having conversations.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How long was that walk?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How far?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that time it look much further than it really was, but I-- I would put it in-- in I would say it was about four or five kilometers still.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he didn't go the whole way with us because I remember at the end of a certain, one kilometer, he turned the other way to go to his school, and we kept going.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would-- we could have gone by train also, but there was more risk, and also it was a question of money.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the point was that he was bragging to us how he had turned in Jewish kids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the Germans had issued rewards, there was a reward of 2,000 Belgian francs for turning in any Jewish person you knew to be in hiding.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In-- in Canadian dollars, at the exchange at the time, I would have said-- I would say that, at that time that would have been the equivalent of about $40 then, which in-- in-- in 1942-- Ironically, that's the right word, the population at large also was not allowed to-- to keep radio sets.",
      "word_count": 54
    }
  ],
